ng d\u1ee5ng ho\u1eb7c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\xean th\u1ee9 ba kh\xe1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 li\xean k\u1ebft, v\xe0 \u0111\xf3ng khung b\xean trong N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng. Ch\xfang t\xf4i c\u0169ng c\xf3 th\u1ec3 tham gia c\xe1c quan h\u1ec7 c\xf9ng ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb v\xe0 c\xe1c quan h\u1ec7 kh\xe1c \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\xe0 c\xe1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\xe0 t\xednh n\u0103ng kh\xe1c cho kh\xe1ch truy c\u1eadp. Nh\u1eefng trang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\xean k\u1ebft n\xe0y c\xf3 c\xe1c ch\xednh s\xe1ch v\u1ec1 quy\u1ec1n ri\xeang t\u01b0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\xe1c bi\u1ec7n ph\xe1p b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt ri\xeang v\xe0 \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\xean th\u1ee9 ba \u0111\xf3 c\xf3 li\xean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi ch\xfang t\xf4i, ch\xfang t\xf4i c\u0169ng kh\xf4ng ki\u1ec3m so\xe1t c\xe1c trang web/\u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\xean k\u1ebft n\xe0y, m\u1ed7i trang \u0111\xf3 c\xf3 c\xe1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\xe1p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 quy\u1ec1n ri\xeang t\u01b0 v\xe0 thu th\u1eadp d\u1eef li\u1ec7u ri\xeang bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp v\u1edbi ch\xfang t\xf4i. D\u1eef li\u1ec7u thu th\u1eadp b\u1edfi c\xe1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\xe1c c\xf9ng ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ch\xfang t\xf4i ho\u1eb7c c\xe1c trang web/\u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\xean th\u1ee9 ba (ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p tr\xean ho\u1eb7c th\xf4ng qua N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a ch\xfang t\xf4i) c\xf3 th\u1ec3 kh\xf4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\xfang t\xf4i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\xe0/ho\u1eb7c l\u01b0u gi\u1eef."}),Object(oe.jsx)("li",{children:"Do \u0111\xf3 ch\xfang t\xf4i kh\xf4ng ch\u1ecbu tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m hay tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\xe1p l\xfd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung, c\xe1c bi\u1ec7n ph\xe1p b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt (ho\u1eb7c s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu bi\u1ec7n ph\xe1p b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt) v\xe0 c\xe1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\xe1c trang web/\u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\xean k\u1ebft n\xe0y. Nh\u1eefng trang web/\u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\xean k\u1ebft n\xe0y ch\u1ec9 v\xec s\u1ef1 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho b\u1ea1n v\xe0 do \u0111\xf3 b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecbu tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m khi truy c\u1eadp ch\xfang. Tuy nhi\xean, ch\xfang t\xf4i t\xecm c\xe1ch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\xednh to\xe0n v\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a ch\xfang t\xf4i v\xe0 c\xe1c li\xean k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t tr\xean t\u1eebng trang web \u0111\xf3 v\xe0 do \u0111\xf3 ch\xfang t\xf4i hoan ngh\xeanh \xfd ki\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i v\u1ec1 c\xe1c trang web \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\xean k\u1ebft n\xe0y (bao g\u1ed3m n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trang web c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 kh\xf4ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng)."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{}),Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),Object(oe.jsx)("h6",{children:"12. C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn v\xe0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i li\xean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c th\xf4ng tin c\xe1 nh\xe2n kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng b\u1ecb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng sai m\u1ee5c \u0111\xedch ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ea1m vi \u0111\xe3 th\xf4ng b\xe1o"}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng c\xf3 quy\u1ec1n g\u1eedi khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i li\xean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\xednh s\xe1ch b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt th\xf4ng tin \u0111\u1ebfn Mioto. Khi ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i n\xe0y, Mioto s\u1ebd x\xe1c nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i th\xf4ng tin, v\xe0 c\xf3 tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i l\xfd do v\xe0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn th\xe0nh vi\xean kh\xf4i ph\u1ee5c v\xe0 b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt l\u1ea1i th\xf4ng tin. C\xe1c b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 sau:"}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i"}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng g\u1eedi khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i cho Mioto theo c\xe1c k\xeanh nh\u01b0 email, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c g\u1eedi v\u0103n b\u1ea3n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a Mioto. B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn CSKH c\u1ee7a Mioto c\xf3 tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn v\xe0 y\xeau c\u1ea7u kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng n\xeau r\xf5 n\u1ed9i dung khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i v\xe0 cung c\u1ea5p c\xe1c th\xf4ng tin, t\xe0i li\u1ec7u c\xf3 li\xean quan."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: X\xe1c minh n\u1ed9i dung khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i"}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"Sau khi ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn, B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn CSKH s\u1ebd c\u0103n c\u1ee9 tr\xean n\u1ed9i dung khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\xe2n lo\u1ea1i v\xe0 chuy\u1ec3n n\u1ed9i dung khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ph\u1ee5 tr\xe1ch \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\xfd."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1eed l\xfd khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i v\xe0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i cho kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng (g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i v\xe0/ho\u1eb7c g\u1eedi email cho kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng)."})]}),Object(oe.jsx)("div",{className:"category-option"}),Object(oe.jsx)("div",{className:"category-option",children:Object(oe.jsx)("h4",{children:"Ch\xednh s\xe1ch & Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh"})}),Object(oe.jsxs)("div",{className:"main-content",children:[Object(oe.jsx)("h6",{children:"1. Tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a kh\xe1ch thu\xea xe v\xe0 ch\u1ee7 xe trong giao d\u1ecbch cho thu\xea xe t\u1ef1 l\xe1i"}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{className:"subtitle",children:"M\u1ee5c \u0111\xedch l\xe2u d\xe0i c\u1ee7a Mioto l\xe0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c x\xe2y d\u1ef1ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng chia s\u1ebb xe \xf4 t\xf4 v\u0103n minh v\xe0 uy t\xedn t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\xec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\xe1c giao d\u1ecbch thu\xea xe trong c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra m\u1ed9t c\xe1ch thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\xe0 th\xe0nh c\xf4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p th\xec vi\u1ec7c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\xe1c b\xean trong tu\xe2n th\u1ee7 c\xe1c ch\xednh s\xe1ch c\u1ee7a Mioto v\xe0 c\xe1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n cam k\u1ebft l\xe0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng."}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["A. Tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 xe",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Giao xe v\xe0 to\xe0n b\u1ed9 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd li\xean quan \u0111\u1ebfn xe \u0111\xfang th\u1eddi gian v\xe0 trong t\xecnh tr\u1ea1ng an to\xe0n, v\u1ec7 sinh s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- C\xe1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd xe li\xean quan bao g\u1ed3m: gi\u1ea5y \u0111\u0103ng k\xfd xe (b\u1ea3n photo c\xf4ng ch\u1ee9ng), gi\u1ea5y ki\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecbnh, gi\u1ea5y b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m xe (b\u1ea3n photo c\xf4ng ch\u1ee9ng ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3n g\u1ed1c).",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Ch\u1ecbu tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\xe1p l\xfd v\u1ec1 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c v\xe0 quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a xe."]}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["B. Tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m kh\xe1ch thu\xea xe",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 xe tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1eadn v\xe0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ho\xe0n tr\u1ea3 xe. K\xed x\xe1c nh\u1eadn bi\xean b\u1ea3n b\xe0n giao v\u1ec1 t\xecnh tr\u1ea1ng xe khi nh\u1eadn v\xe0 khi ho\xe0n tr\u1ea3.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Thanh to\xe1n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1n thu\xea xe cho Ch\u1ee7 xe khi nh\u1eadn xe.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadn xe kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng xu\u1ea5t tr\xecnh \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\xe1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd li\xean quan cho ch\u1ee7 xe: GPLX (ch\u1ee7 xe \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu b\u1ea3n g\u1ed1c v\u1edbi th\xf4ng tin GPLX \u0111\xe3 x\xe1c th\u1ef1c tr\xean app Mioto & g\u1eedi l\u1ea1i), CCCD g\u1eafn chip (ch\u1ee7 xe \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu b\u1ea3n g\u1ed1c v\u1edbi th\xf4ng tin c\xe1 nh\xe2n tr\xean VNeID & g\u1eedi l\u1ea1i) Ho\u1eb7c H\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu (passport) b\u1ea3n g\u1ed1c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc t\xe0i s\u1ea3n th\u1ebf ch\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t (15 tri\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c theo th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 xe) ho\u1eb7c xe m\xe1y c\xf3 gi\xe1 tr\u1ecb t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 15 tri\u1ec7u tr\u1edf l\xean (xe m\xe1y v\xe0 cavet g\u1ed1c) tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1eadn xe.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"-"," ",Object(oe.jsx)("i",{children:Object(oe.jsx)("u",{children:"\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ee7 xe h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\xednh s\xe1ch mi\u1ec5n th\u1ebf ch\u1ea5p:"})})," ","Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng kh\xf4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i t\xe0i s\u1ea3n (xe m\xe1y ho\u1eb7c 15 tri\u1ec7u ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t) khi thu\xea xe c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 xe. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ph\xe1t sinh c\xe1c chi ph\xed kh\xe1c (n\u1ebfu c\xf3) trong qu\xe1 tr\xecnh thu\xea xe, kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng vui l\xf2ng thanh to\xe1n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho ch\u1ee7 xe khi l\xe0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3 xe.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Tu\xe2n th\u1ee7 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\xe0 th\u1eddi gian tr\u1ea3 xe nh\u01b0 2 b\xean \u0111\xe3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Ch\u1ecbu tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec1n b\xf9 m\u1ecdi th\u1ea5t tho\xe1t v\u1ec1 ph\u1ee5 t\xf9ng, ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a xe, \u0111\u1ec1n b\xf9 100% theo gi\xe1 ph\u1ee5 t\xf9ng ch\xednh h\xe3ng n\u1ebfu ph\xe1t hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ee5 t\xf9ng b\u1ecb tr\xe1o \u0111\u1ed5i, ch\u1ecbu 100% chi ph\xed s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa xe n\u1ebfu c\xf3 x\u1ea3y ra h\u1ecfng h\xf3c t\xf9y theo m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u01b0 t\u1ed5n c\u1ee7a xe, chi ph\xed c\xe1c ng\xe0y xe ngh\u1ec9 kh\xf4ng ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c do l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a kh\xe1ch thu\xea xe (gi\xe1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\xednh b\u1eb1ng gi\xe1 thu\xea trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng) v\xe0 c\xe1c kho\u1ea3n ph\xed v\u1ec7 sinh xe n\u1ebfu c\xf3."]}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["C. Tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\xe0 khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Mioto",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),'- Mioto khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb Ch\u1ee7 xe v\xe0 Kh\xe1ch thu\xea xe c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c giao k\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n "H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho thu\xea xe t\u1ef1 l\xe1i" c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\xed k\u1ebft "Bi\xean b\u1ea3n b\xe0n giao xe" nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 2 b\xean trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ph\xe1t sinh tranh ch\u1ea5p.',Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),'- Ch\u1ee7 xe c\xf3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eabu "H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\xea xe t\u1ef1 l\xe1i" v\xe0 "Bi\xean b\u1ea3n b\xe0n giao xe" c\u1ee7a Mioto (vui l\xf2ng cung c\u1ea5p email cho b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn CSKH c\u1ee7a Mioto \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\xf4ng tin).',Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Ch\u1ee7 xe v\xe0 kh\xe1ch thu\xea xe t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecbu to\xe0n b\u1ed9 tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m d\xe2n s\u1ef1 v\xe0 h\xecnh s\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu c\xf3 ph\xe1t sinh tranh ch\u1ea5p gi\u1eefa hai b\xean n\u1ebfu c\xf3. Mioto ch\u1ec9 \u0111\xf3ng vai tr\xf2 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 hai b\xean d\xe0n x\u1ebfp c\xe1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\xe1ch t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t, tu\xe2n theo c\xe1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n, ch\xednh s\xe1ch v\xe0 quy ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea3 hai b\xean \u0111\xe3 cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Mioto."]}),Object(oe.jsx)("h6",{children:"2. Tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Mioto trong c\xe1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ea3y ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 ngo\xe0i \xfd mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0 xe b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m c\u1ed1, th\u1ebf ch\u1ea5p, b\u1ecb b\u1eaft gi\u1eef khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\xf9ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n ma t\xfay, h\xe0ng qu\u1ed1c c\u1ea5m, ho\u1eb7c g\xe2y tai n\u1ea1n"}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Mioto ch\u1ec9 \u0111\xf3ng vai tr\xf2 l\xe0 s\xe0n giao d\u1ecbch th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\u1ec1 cho thu\xea xe \xf4 t\xf4, l\xe0 c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa c\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe v\xe0 kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\xf3 nhu c\u1ea7u thu\xea xe. V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\xe0 to\xe0n b\u1ed9 c\xe1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\xe1t sinh li\xean quan \u0111\u1ebfn giao d\u1ecbch cho thu\xea xe gi\u1eefa ch\u1ee7 xe v\xe0 kh\xe1ch thu\xea s\u1ebd do hai b\xean t\u1ef1 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn, k\xed h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\xe0 ch\u1ecbu tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi nhau.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\xf3 x\u1ea3y ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 ngo\xe0i \xfd mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0 xe b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m c\u1ed1, th\u1ebf ch\u1ea5p, b\u1ecb b\u1eaft khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\xf9ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n ma t\xfay, h\xe0ng qu\u1ed1c c\u1ea5m ho\u1eb7c g\xe2y ra tai n\u1ea1n, Mioto s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\xecnh, gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf vi\u1ec7c h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn ch\u1ee7 xe c\xe1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 tr\xecnh b\xe1o v\u1edbi c\u01a1 quan c\xf4ng an v\xe0 c\xe1c c\u01a1 quan c\xf3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n, cung c\u1ea5p c\xe1c th\xf4ng tin n\u1ebfu c\xf3 li\xean quan \u0111\u1ebfn th\xe0nh vi\xean thu\xea xe ho\u1eb7c c\xe1c th\xf4ng tin kh\xe1c n\u1ebfu c\xf3 y\xeau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb c\u01a1 quan ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng, v\xe0 ti\u1ebfn h\xe0nh kh\xf3a v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n th\xe0nh vi\xean vi ph\u1ea1m.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),'\u0110\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\xe0i s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a m\xecnh v\xe0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\xe1c r\u1ee7i ro c\xf3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, c\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe c\u1ea7n r\xe0ng bu\u1ed9c ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ph\xe1p l\xed b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c giao k\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n "H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho thu\xea xe t\u1ef1 l\xe1i", "Bi\xean b\u1ea3n b\xe0n giao xe" (c\xf3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eabu h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\xe0 bi\xean b\u1ea3n b\xe0n giao do Mioto \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c c\xf3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eabu ri\xeang c\u1ee7a nh\xe0 xe), x\xe1c minh \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\xf4ng tin v\xe0 c\xe1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\xe1 nh\xe2n c\u1ee7a kh\xe1ch thu\xea, gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i t\xe0i s\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc v\xe0 c\xe1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft (v\xe0 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\xf4ng giao c\xe0 v\u1eb9t xe b\u1ea3n ch\xednh cho kh\xe1ch thu\xea). C\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n trang b\u1ecb cho xe thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb GPS \u0111\u1ec3 c\xf3 th\u1ec3 theo d\xf5i v\xe0 ki\u1ec3m tra v\u1ecb tr\xed xe th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\xean nh\u1eb1m c\xf3 c\xe1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \xe1n x\u1eed l\xed k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.',Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"Th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, nh\u1eb1m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1ed9t c\xe1ch to\xe0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a c\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\xe1ch thu\xea, Mioto \u0111ang x\xfac ti\u1ebfn l\xe0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\xe1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\xe1c b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 tri\u1ec3n khai c\xe1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thu\xea xe t\u1ef1 l\xe1i theo ng\xe0y, \xe1p d\u1ee5ng cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\xe1c giao d\u1ecbch cho thu\xea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\xf4ng qua \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Mioto.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"Mioto hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ho\xe0n thi\u1ec7n v\xe0 tri\u1ec3n khai g\xf3i gi\u1ea3i ph\xe1p n\xe0y trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t"]}),Object(oe.jsx)("h6",{id:"canceltrip",children:"3. Ch\xednh s\xe1ch h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn"}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["A. D\xe0nh cho kh\xe1ch thu\xea xe",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),'Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 kh\xe1ng b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn, kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\xf3 th\u1ec3 thao t\xe1c g\u1eedi "Y\xeau c\u1ea7u h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn" tr\xean web/app c\u1ee7a Mioto. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t c\xf3 th\u1ec3, v\xec theo ch\xednh s\xe1ch h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\xf3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ph\xed gi\u1eef ch\u1ed7 cho ch\u1ee7\xa0xe.']}),Object(oe.jsx)(Ms.b,{viewMode:O.h.CP_PRIVACY}),Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ph\xe1t sinh ph\xed h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn, Mioto s\u1ebd tr\u1eeb v\xe0o ph\xed gi\u1eef ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Qu\xfd kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng v\xe0 s\u1ebd thanh to\xe1n l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n n\xe0y cho \u0110\u1ed1i t\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe (v\xe0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0110\u1ed1i t\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn ph\xe1t sinh chi ph\xed \u0111\u1ec1n b\xf9, Mioto s\u1ebd ho\xe0n tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i 100% ph\xed gi\u1eef ch\u1ed7 v\xe0 ti\u1ec1n ph\xed \u0111\u1ec1n b\xf9 cho Qu\xfd kh\xe1ch trong 1 - 3 ng\xe0y l\xe0m vi\u1ec7c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ghi nh\u1eadn th\xf4ng tin s\u1ed1 t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n ng\xe2n h\xe0ng)."}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["B. D\xe0nh cho Ch\u1ee7 xe",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"Nh\u1eb1m gia t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 xe c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a kh\xe1ch thu\xea, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ee7 xe h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn (v\xec l\xed do kh\xf4ng giao \u0111\xfang xe, kh\xf4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o xe, kh\xf4ng \u0111\xfang gi\u1edd), n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 kh\xf4ng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u1eb7c kh\xf4ng c\xf3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \xfd t\u1eeb ph\xeda kh\xe1ch thu\xea, th\xec ch\u1ee7 xe ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\xed h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn cho kh\xe1ch thu\xea theo ch\xednh s\xe1ch h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{})]}),Object(oe.jsx)(Ms.b,{viewMode:O.h.CP_PRIVACY}),Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["Ph\xed h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eeb v\xe0o t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 xe tr\xean Mioto. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p s\u1ed1 d\u01b0 t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 xe nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\xed h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn, ph\u1ea7n ch\xeanh l\u1ec7ch s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \xe2m v\xe0o t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n v\xe0 s\u1ebd c\u1ea5n tr\u1eeb v\xe0o thu nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 xe cho c\xe1c chuy\u1ebfn xe ti\u1ebfp theo.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"B\xean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecbu ph\xed, c\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u1ee7y chuy\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u1ea1m kh\xf3a t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n th\xe0nh vi\xean tr\xean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Mioto.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn CSKH c\u1ee7a Mioto s\u1ebd li\xean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi kh\xe1ch thu\xea xe th\xf4ng b\xe1o v\u1ec1 t\xecnh h\xecnh chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y, v\xe0 ti\u1ebfn h\xe0nh ho\xe0n tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i 100% ti\u1ec1n ph\xed gi\u1eef ch\u1ed7 v\xe0 chi ph\xed \u0111\u1ec1n b\xf9 cho kh\xe1ch (n\u1ebfu c\xf3)."]}),Object(oe.jsx)("h6",{children:"4. Ch\xednh s\xe1ch gi\xe1"}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["A. D\xe0nh cho kh\xe1ch thu\xea xe",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"Tr\xean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Mioto, m\u1ed7i d\xf2ng xe s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho thu\xea t\u1ea1i c\xe1c m\u1ee9c gi\xe1 kh\xe1c nhau t\xf9y thu\u1ed9c v\xe0o s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe v\xe0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\xeam y\u1ebft c\xf4ng khai.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, c\u01a1 c\u1ea5u gi\xe1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\xednh bao g\u1ed3m c\xe1c th\xe0nh ph\u1ea7n:",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- \u0110\u01a1n gi\xe1 thu\xea: L\xe0 gi\xe1 thu\xea ni\xeam y\u1ebft b\u1edfi ch\u1ee7 xe m\xe0 b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\xe0ng nh\xecn th\u1ea5y trong ph\u1ea7n th\xf4ng tin xe. Gi\xe1 thu\xea tr\xean Mioto \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\xednh theo \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t l\xe0 ng\xe0y. Ch\u1ee7 xe c\xf3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh gi\xe1 thu\xea kh\xe1c nhau cho t\u1eebng ng\xe0y, ch\xednh v\xec v\u1eady, chi ph\xed thu\xea xe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\xf3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea3m t\xf9y v\xe0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea1n thu\xea xe. Th\xf4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, gi\xe1 thu\xea s\u1ebd cao h\u01a1n trong d\u1ecbp cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\xe0 c\xe1c ng\xe0y l\u1ec5, t\u1ebft.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u: m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u1ee7 xe c\xf3 ch\xednh s\xe1ch chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u cho c\xe1c chuy\u1ebfn xe k\xe9o d\xe0i 1 tu\u1ea7n ho\u1eb7c 1 th\xe1ng (m\u1ee9c chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u b\xecnh qu\xe2n t\u1eeb 5-20% t\xf9y v\xe0o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 xe). V\xec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\xf3 nhu c\u1ea7u thu\xea xe du l\u1ecbch hay c\xf4ng t\xe1c d\xe0i ng\xe0y, h\xe3y \u01b0u ti\xean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe n\xe0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\xf3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c gi\xe1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Chi ph\xed v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n: n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\xf4ng c\xf3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ecba di\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 xe \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn xe, b\u1ea1n c\xf3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe c\xf3 cung c\u1ea5p th\xeam d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 giao xe t\u1eadn n\u01a1i. Chi ph\xed giao nh\u1eadn xe b\xecnh qu\xe2n t\u1eeb 5.000-15.000 VN\u0110/km t\xf9y v\xe0o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ph\u1ea7n th\xf4ng tin xe v\xe0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed9ng v\xe0o chi ph\xed thu\xea xe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- M\xe3 khuy\u1ebfn m\xe3i: l\xe0 m\xe3 gi\u1ea3m gi\xe1 m\xe0 Mioto g\u1eedi t\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\xe1c th\xe0nh vi\xean c\u1ee7a m\xecnh cho trong c\xe1c \u0111\u1ee3t khuy\u1ebfn m\xe3i, ho\u1eb7c d\xe0nh cho c\xe1c th\xe0nh vi\xean th\xe2n thi\u1ebft giao d\u1ecbch th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\xean tr\xean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Mioto. M\xe3 khuy\u1ebfn m\xe3i n\xe0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eeb tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\xe0o chi ph\xed thu\xea xe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n."]}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"B\u1ea3ng t\xf3m t\u1eaft:"}),Object(oe.jsxs)("div",{className:"tutorial-content--table",children:[Object(oe.jsx)("div",{className:"table-wrap table-wrap-col",children:Object(oe.jsx)("p",{className:"note",children:"Ph\xed thu\xea xe = \u0110\u01a1n gi\xe1 thu\xea ng\xe0y * S\u1ed1 ng\xe0y (Gi\xe1 c\xe1c ng\xe0y c\xf3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i)"})}),Object(oe.jsx)("div",{className:"table-wrap table-wrap-col",children:Object(oe.jsx)("p",{className:"note",children:"Chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u = % Chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u * Ph\xed thu\xea xe"})}),Object(oe.jsx)("div",{className:"table-wrap table-wrap-col",children:Object(oe.jsx)("p",{className:"note",children:"Ph\xed v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n = \u0110\u01a1n gi\xe1 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n * S\u1ed1 km"})}),Object(oe.jsx)("div",{className:"table-wrap table-wrap-col",children:Object(oe.jsx)("p",{className:"note",children:"Khuy\u1ebfn m\xe3i = % Khuy\u1ebfn m\xe3i x (Ph\xed thu\xea xe \u2013 Chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u + Ph\xed v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n)"})})]}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["B. D\xe0nh cho Ch\u1ee7 xe",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"C\xe1c ch\u1ee7 xe c\u1ee7a Mioto \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp gi\xe1 thu\xea xe h\xe0ng ng\xe0y cho th\xe1ng hi\u1ec7n h\xe0nh v\xe0 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 th\xe1ng k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp. B\u1ea1n c\xf3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gi\xe1 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Mioto ho\u1eb7c c\xf3 th\u1ec3 t\xf9y ch\u1ec9nh gi\xe1 cho thu\xea theo mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"- Gi\xe1 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Mioto: \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n 10% so v\u1edbi gi\xe1 thu\xea xe b\xecnh qu\xe2n tr\xean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. M\u1ee9c gi\xe1 n\xe0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn h\xe0nh kh\u1ea3o s\xe1t h\xe0ng th\xe1ng b\u1edfi b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ph\xe1t tri\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Mioto \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u1eebng d\xf2ng xe kh\xe1c nhau."]}),Object(oe.jsx)("h6",{children:"5. Ch\xednh s\xe1ch thanh to\xe1n"}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \xfd cho thu\xea xe t\u1eeb ph\xeda ch\u1ee7 xe, b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thanh to\xe1n Ph\xed gi\u1eef ch\u1ed7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho Mioto 40% Gi\xe1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i ho\u1eb7c 100% Gi\xe1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i. B\u1ea1n c\xf3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a m\u1ee9c Ph\xed gi\u1eef ch\u1ed7 v\xe0 h\xecnh th\u1ee9c thanh to\xe1n chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n qua ng\xe2n h\xe0ng tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn ho\u1eb7c Visa.",Object(oe.jsx)("br",{}),"\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\xecnh th\u1ee9c thanh to\xe1n Ph\xed gi\u1eef ch\u1ed7 l\xe0 40% Gi\xe1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i, ph\u1ea7n Ph\xed c\xf2n l\u1ea1i 60% b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd thanh to\xe1n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho ch\u1ee7 xe ngay khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xe."]}),Object(oe.jsx)("h6",{children:"6. Ch\xednh s\xe1ch th\u1eddi gian giao nh\u1eadn"}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"Th\u1eddi gian thu\xea xe m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp t\u1eeb 9h t\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebfn 8h t\u1ed1i ng\xe0y k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\xean, kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\u0169ng c\xf3 th\u1ec3 t\xf9y ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1eddi gian thu\xea xe theo nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\xecnh, trong v\xf2ng 24 gi\u1edd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\xednh 1 ng\xe0y."}),Object(oe.jsx)("h6",{children:"7. Ch\xednh s\xe1ch k\u1ebft th\xfac s\u1edbm chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i"}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\xfac s\u1edbm chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i c\u1ee7a m\xecnh khi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 xe, \u0111\u1ec3 c\xf3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\xe0n l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n cho c\xe1c ng\xe0y ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, b\u1ea1n n\xean trao \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 xe v\xe0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \xfd t\u1eeb ph\xeda ch\u1ee7 xe. S\u1ed1 ti\u