d d\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n m\xe0 Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng \u0111\xe3 cung c\u1ea5p cho ch\xfang t\xf4i v\xe0/ho\u1eb7c l\u01b0u gi\u1eef v\u1ec1 Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng, cho d\xf9 l\xe0 hi\u1ec7n nay ho\u1eb7c trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\xfap Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\xe1ng su\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi cung c\u1ea5p cho ch\xfang t\xf4i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n n\xe0o. Ch\xednh s\xe1ch n\xe0y c\xf3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\xe0 phi\xean b\u1ea3n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\xean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a ch\xfang t\xf4i. V\xec v\u1eady, ch\xfang t\xf4i khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng n\xean \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 ki\u1ec3m tra Ch\xednh s\xe1ch tr\xean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng."}),Object(oe.jsx)("h6",{children:"1. \u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a"}),Object(oe.jsxs)("p",{children:["- Mioto: L\xe0 ",re.k,", Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u0103ng k\xfd doanh nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ed1 ",re.j,", l\xe0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng/website \u0111\xe3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\xfd v\u1edbi B\u1ed9 C\xf4ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng."]}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"- Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng: l\xe0 (i) c\xe1 nh\xe2n v\xe0/ho\u1eb7c (ii) t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\xf3 cung c\u1ea5p d\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n cho Mioto khi t\xecm ki\u1ebfm, ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn, mua, \u0111\u0103ng k\xfd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, h\xe0ng h\xf3a, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"- S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, h\xe0ng h\xf3a, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5: l\xe0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, h\xe0ng h\xf3a, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 n\xe0o do Mioto cung c\u1ea5p v\xe0/ho\u1eb7c do Mioto h\u1ee3p t\xe1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\xe1c m\xe0 Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng t\xecm ki\u1ebfm, ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn, mua, \u0111\u0103ng k\xfd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"- D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n: l\xe0 th\xf4ng tin d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng k\xfd hi\u1ec7u, ch\u1eef vi\u1ebft, ch\u1eef s\u1ed1, h\xecnh \u1ea3nh, \xe2m thanh ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\xean m\xf4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 ho\u1eb7c gi\xfap x\xe1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n bao g\u1ed3m D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\xe0 D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n bao g\u1ed3m: (i) H\u1ecd, ch\u1eef \u0111\u1ec7m v\xe0 t\xean khai sinh, t\xean g\u1ecdi kh\xe1c (n\u1ebfu c\xf3); (ii) Ng\xe0y, th\xe1ng, n\u0103m sinh; ng\xe0y, th\xe1ng, n\u0103m ch\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c m\u1ea5t t\xedch; (iii) Gi\u1edbi t\xednh; (iv) N\u01a1i sinh, n\u01a1i \u0111\u0103ng k\xfd khai sinh, n\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\xfa, n\u01a1i t\u1ea1m tr\xfa, n\u01a1i \u1edf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, qu\xea qu\xe1n, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 li\xean h\u1ec7; (v) Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch; (vi) H\xecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a c\xe1 nh\xe2n; (vii) S\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, s\u1ed1 ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\xe2n d\xe2n, s\u1ed1 c\u0103n c\u01b0\u1edbc c\xf4ng d\xe2n, s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh danh c\xe1 nh\xe2n, s\u1ed1 h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu, s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea5y ph\xe9p l\xe1i xe, s\u1ed1 bi\u1ec3n s\u1ed1 xe, s\u1ed1 m\xe3 s\u1ed1 thu\u1ebf c\xe1 nh\xe2n, s\u1ed1 b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m x\xe3 h\u1ed9i, s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m y t\u1ebf; (viii) T\xecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\xf4n nh\xe2n; (ix) Th\xf4ng tin v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gia \u0111\xecnh (cha m\u1eb9, con c\xe1i,v\u1ee3, ch\u1ed3ng, \u2026) v\xe0 th\xf4ng tin v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\xe1 nh\xe2n c\xf3 li\xean quan v\xed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\xe1m h\u1ed9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\xean h\u1ec7, \u2026; (x) Th\xf4ng tin v\u1ec1 t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\xe1 nh\xe2n; (xi) C\xe1c th\xf4ng tin kh\xe1c g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 ho\u1eb7c gi\xfap x\xe1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 kh\xf4ng thu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea1m vi D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\xe1p lu\u1eadt. (xii) D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n kh\xe1c theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\xe1p lu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i t\u1eebng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"- D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: l\xe0 D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n ri\xeang t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng m\xe0 khi b\u1ecb x\xe2m ph\u1ea1m s\u1ebd g\xe2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n v\xe0 l\u1ee3i \xedch h\u1ee3p ph\xe1p c\u1ee7a Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng, bao g\u1ed3m c\xe1c lo\u1ea1i d\u1eef li\u1ec7u sau: (i) Th\xf4ng tin li\xean quan t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 trung gian thanh to\xe1n, bao g\u1ed3m: th\xf4ng tin \u0111\u1ecbnh danh kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\xe1p lu\u1eadt, th\xf4ng tin v\u1ec1 t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n, th\xf4ng tin th\u1ebb ng\xe2n h\xe0ng, d\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed giao d\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n ng\xe2n h\xe0ng; th\xf4ng tin t\xe0i ch\xednh, t\xedn d\u1ee5ng v\xe0 c\xe1c th\xf4ng tin v\u1ec1 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, l\u1ecbch s\u1eed giao d\u1ecbch t\xe0i ch\xednh, ch\u1ee9ng kho\xe1n, b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng t\u1ea1i c\xe1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\xedn d\u1ee5ng, chi nh\xe1nh ng\xe2n h\xe0ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\xe0i, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c cung \u1ee9ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 trung gian thanh to\xe1n, ch\u1ee9ng kho\xe1n, b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m, c\xe1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\xe9p kh\xe1c; (ii) D\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\xed c\u1ee7a Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\xe1c \u0111\u1ecbnh qua d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb; (iii) D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n kh\xe1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\xe1p lu\u1eadt quy \u0111\u1ecbnh l\xe0 \u0111\u1eb7c th\xf9 v\xe0 c\u1ea7n c\xf3 bi\u1ec7n ph\xe1p b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft; (iv) C\xe1c th\xf4ng tin kh\xe1c g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 ho\u1eb7c gi\xfap x\xe1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\xe1ch h\xe0ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\xe1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\xe0 D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ph\xe1p lu\u1eadt."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"- X\u1eed l\xfd D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n: l\xe0 m\u1ed9t ho\u1eb7c nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\xe1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n, nh\u01b0: thu th\u1eadp, ghi, ph\xe2n t\xedch, x\xe1c nh\u1eadn, l\u01b0u tr\u1eef, ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda, c\xf4ng khai, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p, truy c\u1eadp, truy xu\u1ea5t, thu h\u1ed3i, m\xe3 h\xf3a, gi\u1ea3i m\xe3, sao ch\xe9p, chia s\u1ebb, truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0a, cung c\u1ea5p, chuy\u1ec3n giao, x\xf3a, h\u1ee7y d\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n ho\u1eb7c c\xe1c h\xe0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\xe1c c\xf3 li\xean quan theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\xe1p lu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i t\u1eebng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"- B\xean Ki\u1ec3m so\xe1t D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n: l\xe0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\xe1 nh\xe2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c \u0111\xedch v\xe0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n X\u1eed l\xfd D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"- B\xean X\u1eed l\xfd D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n: l\xe0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\xe1 nh\xe2n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c X\u1eed l\xfd D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n thay m\u1eb7t cho B\xean Ki\u1ec3m so\xe1t d\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n, th\xf4ng qua m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi B\xean Ki\u1ec3m so\xe1t d\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 nh\xe2n."}),Object(oe.jsx)("p",{children:"- B\xean Ki\u1ec3m so\xe1t v\xe0 x\u1eed l\xfd D\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\xe1 