h k\u1ef3",desc:"Xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ecbnh k\xec 5.000 km, gi\xfap xe ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\xe0 b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9.",icon:s.p+"static/media/reason5.a79ed786.svg"},{id:6,title:"Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n",desc:"\u0110\u0103ng k\xfd d\u1ec5 d\xe0ng, quy tr\xecnh nhanh ch\xf3ng, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eadn t\xecnh.",icon:s.p+"static/media/reason6.269d2a56.svg"}],Qb=[{id:1,title:"\u0110i\u1ec1n th\xf4ng tin \u0111\u0103ng k\xfd",desc:"\u0110i\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\xf4ng tin theo m\u1eabu \u0111\u0103ng k\xfd.",icon:Object(oe.jsx)(ee.If,{}),isActionForm:!0},{id:2,title:"T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n & b\xe1o ph\xed",desc:"Sau khi nh\u1eadn th\xf4ng tin, Micarro s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng li\xean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, quy tr\xecnh cho thu\xea & g\u1eedi b\xe1o ph\xed theo t\u1eebng d\xf2ng xe.",icon:Object(oe.jsx)(ee.a,{})},{id:3,title:"K\xfd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng & cho thu\xea",desc:"Trong v\xf2ng 1-2 ng\xe0y l\xe0m vi\u1ec7c, sau khi hai b\xean \u0111\xe3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t c\xe1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n, Micarro s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\xe0nh k\xfd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng & b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1eadn h\xe0nh cho thu\xea xe.",icon:Object(oe.jsx)(ee.g,{})}],zb=[{id:1,question:"1. N\u1ebfu xe b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, ai s\u1ebd chi tr\u1ea3 chi ph\xed?",answer:"Micarro thanh to\xe1n 100% chi ph\xed ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i & b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 m\u1ed7i 5000km trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eadn h\xe0nh."},{id:2,question:"2. T\xf4i c\xf3 th\u1ec3 thanh l\xfd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng s\u1edbm kh\xf4ng?",answer:"C\xf3. Ch\u1ee7 xe ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\xf4ng b\xe1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc 30 ng\xe0y \u0111\u1ec3 Micarro s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp thanh l\xfd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng."},{id:3,question:"3. Hao m\xf2n xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\xednh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\xe0o?",answer:"C\xe